<p id="fs-idp52331904">(a) hydrogen fluoride, HF</p>
<p id="fs-idp52332288">(b) ammonia, NH<sub>3</sub></p>
<p id="fs-idp70670144">(c) nitric acid, HNO<sub>3</sub></p>
