<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idp40477296">
<p id="fs-idp40477552">Determine which of the following contains the greatest mass of hydrogen: 1 mol of CH<sub>4</sub>, 0.6 mol of C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>6</sub>, or 0.4 mol of C<sub>3</sub>H<sub>8</sub>.</p>
