<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idp41347392">
<p id="fs-idp41347648">One 55-gram serving of a particular cereal supplies 270 mg of sodium, 11% of the recommended daily allowance. How many moles and atoms of sodium are in the recommended daily allowance?</p>
